# Add, edit, and delete a supplier

## Add a supplier

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Suppliers/Supplier List** tab.
2. Click the **Add** button.
3. Fill in the required Supplier details.
4. Click **Publish** to save and add the supplier.

## Edit a supplier

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, go to the **Suppliers/Supplier List** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the Supplier you want to edit.
3. Make the necessary changes to the Supplier details.
4. Click **Publish** to save your changes.

## Delete a supplier

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Suppliers/Supplier List** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the Supplier you want to delete.
3. Click the **Delete** button in the top-right corner of the screen.
4. In the confirmation popup, click **Confirm** to finalize the deletion.